{
  "stem": "9898.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were staying there in the woods, very close to the border of East Prussia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "September 1, 1939, at 3 o'clock in the morning, we received artillery fire, very heavy artillery fire, from the German side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The war started.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We found a lot of spies at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For example, the man who was on the railroad station was giving different information to the German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because all Pomerania, there were a lot of Germans, because they belonged to Germany, as I mentioned before-- before the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were under heavy artillery fire for almost two days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after two days, we start to move back, the whole army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were moving mostly during the night, because during the day, as I can remember, the Germans were-- the German-- they call it Luftwaffe, the German Air Force-- was attacking us tremendously.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had fantastic planes, not their owns, the Czechoslovakian planes, the Stukas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were attacking us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day-- I remember it very well too-- I almost got killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The last second almost, I got into a deep-- into a hole, and the planes were over our heads.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we kept moving because they were attacking us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We even didn't have the big tanks in our army-- small tankettes, and they came with these big Tiger tanks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we didn't have any chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're moving back until we came to Kutno.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, Kutno was south of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not far from Wloclawek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why I mention this, because my parents had to run away from [NON-ENGLISH] because the Germans occupy there, and they knew that they would get into big trouble under the Germans, under the Hitler.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
